        <paragraph id="1">
            <sentence id="1.1">Created attachment 122536
screenshot of drop down list not cleared by LO Calc</sentence>
        </paragraph>
        <paragraph id="2">
            <sentence id="2.1">After right clicking on a cell to get the drop down options, e.g. Copy, Paste, etc. and left clicking on one of the options, e.g. Copy, the portion of the drop down list is still visible.</sentence>
